name: DAWG
description: $DAWG is the official token of the Doge Capital ecosystem. Doge Capital is a NFT collection on the Solana blockchain consisting of 5000 unique NFTs including utility airdrops along with the $DAWG token at its core. This token can be earned by staking the Doge Capital NFTs and additional airdrops per day(5 $DAWG tokens for staking a Doge NFT and 1 $DAWG token per additional NFT, per day). Withdrawing the $DAWG token rewards from the website will unstake all NFTs and burn 1 airdrop token. The token will also serve as a currency for different utilities within the Doge Capital ecosystem like buying exclusive Merchandise, changing NFT metadata, member exclusive events etc.
